{"data":[{"date":"11:47 14/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan 16h ng\u00e0y 14/8 (Asiad 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/link-xem-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-pakistan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Pakistan v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 14/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng cao nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd v\u1eeba b\u01b0\u1edbc ra t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nH\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine, Oman v\u00e0 Uzbekistan c\u00e0ng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Pakistan link xem Asiad 2018 HD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Pakistan link xem Asiad 2018 HD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/vietnam-pakistan-2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Pakistan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 ASIAD tr\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh 1 trong hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D.\u00a0 D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c k\u1ef7 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Indonesia d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu tinh th\u1ea7n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, trong 3 ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t Indonesia, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u00e2n c\u1ecf nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, do s\u00e2n c\u1ecf m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ee7a Samsung t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Java ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u2018t\u1eadp chay\u2019 tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t xi m\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (14/8).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u an \u1ee7i l\u00e0 trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o nhau gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0 l\u00f2ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a NHM.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ASIAD, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m \u2018thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi kinh nghi\u1ec7m\u2019. Ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. R\u1ea5t may \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang seo c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o may m\u1eafn.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5468","checkdouble":"194453"},{"date":"11:55 14/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan: Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 t\u00edch m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-khoi-dau-ky-tich-moi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn cho r\u1eb1ng k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n hai. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ee9ng minh th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 may m\u1eafn.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/link-xem-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-pakistan-372-194453.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/link-xem-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/link-xem-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-pakistan-372-194453.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan 16h ng\u00e0y 14/8 (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1eeb k\u1ef3 t\u00edch U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ebfn ASIAD 2018</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, khi m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta \u1edf c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Australia v\u00e0 Syria.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Miura \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 3 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Jordan, UAE v\u00e0 \u00dac, qua \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Miura b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sa th\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn xa h\u01a1n, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng \u00edt gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u00f9ng c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111i t\u1eeb h\u1ebft b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0y sang b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u01afCV v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 t\u00edch m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 t\u00edch m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/30/Xem-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Pakistan-Khoi-dau-ky-tich-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 t\u00edch v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u1eafng h\u1eadu \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 t\u00edch v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u1eafng h\u1eadu trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi ch\u00fang ta t\u1eeb t\u00e2m th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng &lsquo;l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng&rsquo; \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 t\u00edch l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u n\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ea7n hai v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo, khi m\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u00ecn h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng &lsquo;l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng&rsquo;. Khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch c\u1eb7n k\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD n\u0103m nay gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng hay Toshiya Miura \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u1edf hai k\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111i xa t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2u m\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111ang c\u1ea7n l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i b\u1edfi m\u1ecdi t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Kyrgyzstan, Malaysia v\u00e0 Bahrain. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/olympic-vietnam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 b\u1edfi U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u00e2u \u00c1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Do \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o k\u1ef3 t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o k\u1ef3 t\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebfn. V\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c hay kh\u00f4ng v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u00f2n l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng g\u1eb7p Pakistan v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 14/8. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i s\u1ebd c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec, v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c, th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Khi th\u1ea7y Park t\u1ef1 tin<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y xu\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin cho bi\u1ebft: : &ldquo;\u0110\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra khi V-League v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac, n\u00ean t\u00f4i tin l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u1edf m\u1ee9c cao. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua c\u0169ng gi\u00fap to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD 2018&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam Park Hang Seo\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam Park Hang Seo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/binhluan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 trang b\u1ecb cho&nbsp;Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 tin \u1edf ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1 v\u00e0 Trung \u00c1. To\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang 2 l\u1ea7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Quang H\u1ea3i, Duy M\u1ea1nh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng,&hellip; th\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a 3 &lsquo;l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng&rsquo; Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u0169ng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, s\u1eafc b\u00e9n trong d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. H\u01a1n h\u1ebft, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. &lsquo;S\u00fang \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean n\u00f2ng&rsquo;, v\u00e0 h\u00e3y ch\u1edd xem m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau-168-194432.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau-168-194432.html\">Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?</span><br>\r\nC\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ebd theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi VTV kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 14/8): Chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch</span><br>\r\nNHM n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5467","checkdouble":"194454"},{"date":"09:02 14/08","title":"Sao Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu Conte c\u00f2n \u1edf l\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/11/sao-chelsea-khang-dinh-da-ra-di-neu-conte-con-o-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u0169 nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng, anh m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c to\u00e0n t\u00e2m to\u00e0n \u00fd cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chuy\u1ec7n Antonio Conte v\u00e0 Willian kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u01b0a th\u00edch nhau v\u1ed1n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec m\u1edbi l\u1ea1 qua hai n\u0103m tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd \u1edf Stamford Bridge. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil hi\u1ebfm khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 kh\u00e1c.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u1edd khi Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i th\u00ec Willian c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea5u gi\u1ebfm v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y n\u1ebfu Conte c\u0169ng v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng \u00e1? Kh\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Conte T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Chelsea n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Conte T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Chelsea n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/sao-chelsea-khang-dinh-da-ra-di-neu-conte-con-o-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Conte</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri thay th\u1ebf ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng, Willian c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1eefa. Anh n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cT\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u h\u1ebft c\u1ea3, tr\u1eeb khi CLB mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n t\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i to\u00e0n t\u00e2m to\u00e0n \u00fd cho n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t m\u1edbi m\u1ebb \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi \u2013 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, HLV m\u1edbi, tri\u1ebft l\u00fd m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chelsea ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb \u1edf Premier League 2018/19 v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 3-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Willian c\u0169ng t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u00e0y: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n li\u1ec1n, m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u00edt nh\u1ea5t duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp theo tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal.\u201d \u2013 Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn derby London \u1edf Stamford Bridge cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/willian-gat-bo-on-ao-chinh-phuc-dinh-cao-389-194108.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/willian-gat-bo-on-ao-chinh-phuc-dinh-cao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/willian-gat-bo-on-ao-chinh-phuc-dinh-cao-389-194108.html\">Willian: G\u1ea1t b\u1ecf \u1ed3n \u00e0o, chinh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec9nh cao</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 6 c\u1ee7a Willian t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. V\u00e0 ch\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00f3c x\u00f9, \u201cqu\u1ea3n ca\u201d c\u1ee7a The Blues, m\u1ed9t tay tr\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 ngh\u1ec1 v\u00e0 h\u00f4m nay ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5466","checkdouble":"194434"},{"date":"09:37 14/08","title":"Man Utd s\u1eafp c\u00f3 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/man-utd-sap-co-giam-doc-bong-da-dau-tien-trong-lich-su.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man Utd s\u1eafp c\u00f3 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed nh\u1eb1m th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Edwin Van Der Sar v\u00e0 Monchi l\u00e0 hai \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</h2><h2>Man Utd s\u1eafp c\u00f3 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo xu h\u01b0\u1edbng chung c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Man Utd s\u1eafp c\u00f3 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u00ean tr\u00e1ch v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi David Moyes, Van Gaal cho \u0111\u1ebfn Jose Mourinho l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o &quot;qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&quot; \u0111i theo xu h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh chung c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u CLB t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man Utd sap co giam doc bong da dau tien trong lich su voi Van Der Sar la mot trong nhung ung cu vien.\" title=\"Man Utd s\u1eafp c\u00f3 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi Van Der Sar l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/man-utd-sap-co-giam-doc-bong-da-dau-tien-trong-lich-su.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Man Utd s\u1eafp c\u00f3 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi Van Der Sar l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u0110 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Man Utd s\u1ebd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng Ph\u00f3 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Ed Woodward v\u00e0 HLV Mourinho trong v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Vi\u1ec7c &quot;ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t&quot; ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Man Utd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed5 sung c\u01a1 c\u1ea5u l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Daily Mail ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Man Utd \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0a hai \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch l\u00e0 Edwin Van Der Sar v\u00e0 Monchi. M\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Fabio Paratici c\u1ee7a Juventus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 ba \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean, Edwin Van Der Sar l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Man Utd k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. C\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1i Ajax, t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League 2007-08 c\u00f9ng Man Utd.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ee8ng vi\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai l\u00e0 Monchi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng G\u0110 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Monchi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Sevilla trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a AS Roma c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh t\u1eeb v\u1ecb G\u0110 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fabio Paratici tuy \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1ec1 Juventus trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Juventus c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Serie A.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Man Utd m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-se-tro-lai-old-trafford-vao-dau-nam-2019-172-194383.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2019</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\">Man Utd m\u1edf m\u00e0n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb: Kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7? Kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bo-doi-ngoi-sao-se-quyet-dinh-thanh-bai-cua-mu-172-194213.html\">B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alexis-sanchez-trai-long-ve-nua-nam-khon-kho-o-old-trafford-172-194211.html\">Alexis Sanchez tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 n\u1eeda n\u0103m kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 \u1edf Old Trafford</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-man-utd-khong-manh-len-chut-nao-het-172-194205.html\">Mourinho: &ldquo;Man Utd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean ch\u00fat n\u00e0o h\u1ebft&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dong-thai-cho-thay-marcos-rojo-chuan-bi-chia-tay-man-utd-172-194200.html\">\u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i cho th\u1ea5y Marcos Rojo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chia tay Man Utd</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5465","checkdouble":"194439"},{"date":"09:53 14/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u Emery \u0111ang l\u00e0m g\u00ec v\u1edbi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/huyen-thoai-khong-hieu-emery-dang-lam-gi-voi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tony Adams k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00ec nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd trong tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac trong th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda khi Arsenal nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i hai b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110KV\u0110 Man City ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, hai t\u00e2n binh Bernd Leno v\u00e0 Lucas Torreira b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u1ec9 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/huyen-thoai-khong-hieu-emery-dang-lam-gi-voi-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 c\u1ef1u trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Tony Adams l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Emery: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Xhaka, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n Torreira, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecf con nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng minh, \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u00fang ta v\u00e0 t\u00f4i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh vai tr\u00f2 v\u1edbi N\u2019Golo Kante \u1edf Chelsea c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea1i sao Leno kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong khung th\u00e0nh c\u01a1 ch\u1ee9? T\u00f4i y\u00eau qu\u00fd Cech, m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0ng th\u00f4i n\u00e0o, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi r\u1ed3i. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u1ea3 Maitland-Niles \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i n\u1eefa, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb non n\u1edbt kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Man City? Th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i t\u1edbi gi\u1edd v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u Emery \u0111ang l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u1edf Arsenal su\u1ed1t 5-6 tu\u1ea7n qua. N\u1ebfu l\u00e0 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m th\u00ec h\u1eb3n t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t n\u00f3ng m\u1eaft v\u1edbi anh ta l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: B\u00ecnh m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u ch\u01b0a m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. V\u00e0 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5464","checkdouble":"194441"},{"date":"10:35 14/08","title":"T\u00e2n binh Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen hay h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/chuyen-ve-naby-keita-phan-1-vua-cua-duong-pho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Bruce Grobbelaar nh\u01b0 ph\u00e1t cu\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Naby Keita trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u00fap Liverpool \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng West Ham ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Keita g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh \u1edf Liverpool</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda \u1edf Anh v\u00e0 t\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft l\u1ea1i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Liverpool l\u00e0 CLB g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 4 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Naby Keita, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ng\u01b0\u1eddi Guinea v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201c\u0111\u1eb7t g\u1ea1ch\u201d t\u1eeb RB Leipzig h\u1ed3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i Steven Gerrard, Keita nhanh ch\u00f3ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a The Kop. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u00fap Liverpool \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng West Ham ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Naby Keita c\u1ee7a Liverpool xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Kante h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Naby Keita c\u1ee7a Liverpool xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Kante h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/chuyen-ve-naby-keita-phan-1-vua-cua-duong-pho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Naby Keita c\u1ee7a Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n hay ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf c\u1ea3 4 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh Keita m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn. T\u00e2n binh 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1eeb thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o b\u1ea5t t\u1eadn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Keita to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Kante<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Bruce Grobbelaar nh\u01b0 ph\u00e1t cu\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Keita v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1ea1nh mi\u1ec7ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 N\u2019Golo Kante, ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 hay nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-ve-naby-keita-phan-1-vua-cua-duong-pho-172-194447.html\">Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 Naby Keita (Ph\u1ea7n 1): Vua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Zimbabwe: \u201cTh\u00e0nh th\u1ef1c m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Keita l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 c\u1ee7a Liverpool sau th\u1eddi Gerrard \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u1ede Keita, \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn \u1edf Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi. HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o khi nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Keita \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch so s\u00e1nh Keita v\u1edbi Kante, m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Kante c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng, c\u00f2n Keita l\u1ea1i to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n h\u01a1n, khi v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu h\u1ed3i, v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ghi b\u00e0n ho\u1eb7c ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c 1/3 cu\u1ed1i s\u00e2n nh\u00ecn gi\u1ed1ng h\u1ec7t Coutinho ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-40-west-ham-lu-doan-do-bay-cao-cung-deco-de-nhi-172-194352.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/liverpool-40-west-ham-lu-doan-do-bay-cao-cung-deco-de-nhi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-40-west-ham-lu-doan-do-bay-cao-cung-deco-de-nhi-172-194352.html\">Liverpool 4-0 West Ham: L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf bay cao c\u00f9ng \u201cDeco \u0111\u1ec7 nh\u1ecb\u201d</span><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League. S\u1ebd th\u1eadt thi\u1ebfu s\u00f3t n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi \u201cDeco \u0111\u1ec7 nh\u1ecb\u201d c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Naby...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/naby-keita-ra-mat-an-tuong-cai-gia-cua-su-cho-doi-172-194365.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/naby-keita-ra-mat-an-tuong-cai-gia-cua-su-cho-doi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/naby-keita-ra-mat-an-tuong-cai-gia-cua-su-cho-doi-172-194365.html\">Naby Keita ra m\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng: C\u00e1i gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i</span><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111ang thu v\u1ec1 c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng, Naby Keita nh\u01b0 th\u1ee9 linh ki\u1ec7n c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu cho c\u1ed7 m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a Jurgen Klopp v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh tr\u01a1n tru h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5463","checkdouble":"194443"},{"date":"07:41 14/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 14/8): Chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>NHM n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan.</h2><h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; Khi kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng cao nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd v\u1eeba b\u01b0\u1edbc ra t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine, Oman v\u00e0 Uzbekistan c\u00e0ng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 ASIAD tr\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh 1 trong hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D. &nbsp;<o:p></o:p>D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c k\u1ef7 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 148) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 148) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Indonesia d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu tinh th\u1ea7n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, trong 3 ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t Indonesia, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u00e2n c\u1ecf nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, do s\u00e2n c\u1ecf m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ee7a Samsung t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Java ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 &lsquo;t\u1eadp chay&rsquo; tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t xi m\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (14/8).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u an \u1ee7i l\u00e0 trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o nhau gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0 l\u00f2ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a NHM.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ASIAD, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m &lsquo;thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi kinh nghi\u1ec7m&rsquo;. Ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. R\u1ea5t may \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang seo c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o may m\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 &lsquo;\u1ea9n s\u1ed1&rsquo; Olympic Pakistan<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pakistan c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi su\u1ed1t 3 n\u0103m qua, h\u1ecd b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sau \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb L\u0110B\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi FIFA.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 n\u0103m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pakistan &lsquo;\u00e2m th\u1ea7m luy\u1ec7n c\u00f4ng&rsquo; \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ASIAD 2018 - gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea5p ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Nam \u00c1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1.&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khan hi\u1ebfm th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y song r\u1ea5t may m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9n b\u0103ng ghi h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Pakistan t\u1ea1i Bahrain m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n th\u00f4ng tin qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eafm r\u00f5 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ban \u0111\u1ea7u, Pakistan kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n hung tin khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kaleemullah Khan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i xin h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n mu\u1ed9n v\u00ec v\u01b0\u1edbng b\u1eadn th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 Pakistan t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng anh kh\u00f4ng coi tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0u c\u1edd s\u1eafc \u00e1o.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Olympic Pakistan\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Pakistan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Cac-doi-thu-tai-ASIAD-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-manh-yeu-the-nao-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Pakistan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Olympic Pakistan c\u00f3 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 20 tu\u1ed5i. Ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Saddam Hussain. &nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hussain hi\u1ec7n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Larnaka Gencler Birligi S.K, CLB c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea3o S\u00edp. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i (c\u00f9ng Yousuf Butt) trong l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Pakistan. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 19 tr\u1eadn cho \u0110T Pakistan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn chung, \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Pakistan ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. C\u00f2n v\u1ec1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1ee9 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 khi\u00eam nh\u01b0\u1eddng. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00eam ASIAD v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1 th\u1eafng, 2 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 1 thua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. Trong cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o ch\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 - 4 - 3. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 qu\u00e1 l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n&nbsp;\u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng, ch\u00fang ta ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch Palestien hay Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf&nbsp;gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u.T\u1ef1 tin nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 quan, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng s\u01a1 h\u1edf, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:&#xA;115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan: 2-0<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:&nbsp;</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>+ Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng; Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, V\u0103n Thanh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu; \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft; Quang H\u1ea3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>+ Olympic Pakistan: Saqib Hanif; Mohsin Ali, Umar Hayat, Mohammad Sohail, Muhammad Bilal; Khan Niazi, Saddam Hussain, Basit Amin, Mehmood Khan; Mohammad Riaz, Maqbool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-khi-thay-park-da-lo-het-168-194191.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-khi-thay-park-da-lo-het.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-khi-thay-park-da-lo-het-168-194191.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD: Khi th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u00e3 lo h\u1ebft</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa. V\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y NHM c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, khi m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 lo...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5462","checkdouble":"194428"},{"date":"07:57 14/08","title":"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ebd theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi VTV kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, do m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed ch\u00e0o b\u00e1n b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u2018b\u00e1n l\u1ebb\u2019 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00ean \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam VTV \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c NHM ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo th\u00f4ng qua internet. Song NHM s\u1ebd xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Xem-truc-tiep-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Pakistan-o-dau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>NHM c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan tr\u00ean trang vidio.com.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00f4ng qua website vidio.com.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 website ph\u00e1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ASIAD 2018 \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem vidio.com l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c k\u00ec ASIAD tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Website n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfu tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam trong c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y t\u1eeb 10/8 \u0111\u1ebfn 12/8 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h ng\u00e0y 14/8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, website vidio.com d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Pakistan./.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:\n10.0pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 14/8): Chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch</span><br>\r\nNHM n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5461","checkdouble":"194432"},{"date":"08:15 14/08","title":"C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-dat-niem-tin-vao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u nay, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: &quot;Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u hanh th\u00f4ng. Pakistan kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh. G\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1ecb c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 kh\u00ed h\u1eadu n\u1eafng n\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang ta v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n V.League kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. C\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp trung ngay, l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i &quot;T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng&quot; v\u1eeba qua, n\u00ean t\u00f4i lo h\u1ecd b\u1ecb b\u00e0o m\u00f2n&quot;, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111ang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u00f2n chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Theo \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ecb n\u00e0y tin t\u01b0\u1edfng HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti (Cikarang). Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y, mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 14/8): Chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch</span><br>\r\nNHM n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau-168-194432.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau-168-194432.html\">Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?</span><br>\r\nC\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ebd theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi VTV kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5460","checkdouble":"194436"},{"date":"08:31 14/08","title":"HLV Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/14/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-truoc-cuoc-so-tai-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, HLV Jose Antonio Noguira c\u1ee7a Pakistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>HLV Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u0129 nhi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/HLV-PAKISTAN-5-8912-1534142888-8699-1534156883.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Olympic Pakistan (gi\u1eefa) th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh HLV Jose Antonio Noguira, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Pakistan th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 xem b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh \u1edf l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i 23. \u0110\u1ed9i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Park Hang-seo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c do ba n\u0103m qua kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf do \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb FIFA.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &quot;\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 ba&nbsp;n\u0103m qua Pakistan kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng gh\u00ea g\u1edbm. T\u00f4i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Pakistan v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y t\u1eeb c\u00e1c l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft t\u00f4i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Antonio Noguira c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Olympic Pakistan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd tranh t\u00e0i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u00edch lu\u1ef9 kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n cao nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 quan trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti (Cikarang). Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y, mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 14/8): Chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch</span><br>\r\nNHM n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau-168-194432.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau-168-194432.html\">Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?</span><br>\r\nC\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ebd theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi VTV kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5459","checkdouble":"194438"},{"date":"08:11 14/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 14/8: M.U s\u1eafp ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong m\u01a1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-148-mu-sap-hoan-tat-ban-hop-dong-trong-mo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 14/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Barca \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Dembele.</strong> Barcelona s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eafng nghe nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho Ousmane Dembele. Sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi ch\u00ecm trong nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n. Barca mu\u1ed1n thanh l\u00fd Dembele \u0111\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M.U s\u1eafp ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong m\u01a1. </strong>Man United t\u1ef1 tin David de Gea s\u1ebd k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi thay cho giao k\u00e8o c\u0169 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 n\u0103m. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 180 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 148 MU s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi De Gea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 148 MU s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi De Gea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-148-MU-sap-gia-han-voi-De-Gea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M.U t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng De Gea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Atletico v\u00e0 Dortmund quan t\u00e2m sao Tottenham. </strong>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Serge Aurier t\u1ea1i Tottenham b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i l\u00ean c\u1ee7a Kieran Trippier. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 Dortmund \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Liverpool xem x\u00e9t b\u00e1n Klavan. </strong>Liverpool \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 Ragnar Klavan ra \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 8. L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch tinh gi\u1ea3n bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 Klavan n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Modric \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p tin \u0111\u1ed3n Inter.</strong> Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Inter Milan \u0111ang g\u1eedi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u00e0o m\u1eddi h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn t\u1eeb Real, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Modric v\u1eabn \u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric\" title=\"Luka Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Chi-75-trieu-bang,-Real-Madrid-mua-Christian-Eriksen-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Modric v\u00e0o tay Inter</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>B\u1ed9 ba \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh theo \u0111u\u1ed5i sao tr\u1ebb Real. </strong>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh l\u00e0 Middlebrough, Derby v\u00e0 Aston Villa \u0111\u1ec1u d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m cho Martin Odegaard. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i \u01b0u ti\u00ean n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Real song chi\u1ec1u mua c\u00e1c CLB Premier League \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nInter m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u sao tr\u1ebb Barca. </strong>Keita Balde m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Inter Milan d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m t\u1eeb Monaco. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia c\u00e0i v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i Barcelona trong 7 n\u0103m (2004 t\u1edbi 2011) v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Gameiro r\u1eddi Atletico gia nh\u1eadp Valencia. </strong>Valencia th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kevin Gameiro t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid. \u0110\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \"B\u1ea7y d\u01a1i\" \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 16 tri\u1ec7u Euro. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5458","checkdouble":"194435"},{"date":"07:51 14/08","title":"Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u201cb\u00e1o th\u00f9\u201d Barca th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ngc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/12/6/roma-chuan-bi-bao-thu-barca-thanh-cong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Roma s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Steven N'Zonzi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1eeb Sevilla v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i \u201cb\u00e1o th\u00f9\u201d m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia d\u00e0nh cho Barca sau khi cu\u1ed7m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Malcom t\u1eeb tay h\u1ecd.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca quan t\u00e2m N'Zonzi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSteven N'Zonzi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Sevilla t\u1eeb Stoke City m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2015 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. Anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Sevilla 3 n\u0103m qua, c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League m\u00f9a 2015/16.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, N'Zonzi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Sevilla c\u00f2n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u bao g\u1ed3m Barcelona v\u00e0 AS Roma \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Steven NZonzi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Roma s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Steven NZonzi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/6/david-moyes-tuyen-bo-pha-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca quan t\u00e2m Steven N'Zonzi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, N'Zonzi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec7 \u0111\u01a1n xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i l\u00ean l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Sevilla. Sau 3 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, anh mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. N'Zonzi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Sevilla tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng Roma m\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 ph\u00f9 th\u1ee7y chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Monchi, Roma \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u00fang ra h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Malcom t\u1eeb Bordeaux n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb Barca ra tay c\u01b0\u1edbp \u0111i ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3n chi n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u00f4 h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u00e1o th\u00f9 Barca th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ngc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u00e1o th\u00f9 Barca th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ngc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Roma-chuan-bi-bao-thu-Barca-thanh-congc-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u01b0ng Roma s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Steven N'Zonzi nh\u1edd t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Monchi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Roma s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Steven N'Zonzi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00f2n \u201cb\u00e1o th\u00f9\u201d th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Barca. S\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Monchi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0a m\u00ecnh t\u1edbi Sevilla tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y khi\u1ebfn N'Zonzi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua. Anh ng\u00f3 l\u01a1 s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb Barca hay Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 N'Zonzi, Roma s\u1ebd ti\u00eau t\u1ed1n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam 5 tri\u1ec7u ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed t\u00f9y v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh t\u00edch. Gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u00e0 Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 1988 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Roma tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/roma-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-arsenal-172-193727.html\">Roma b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-so-1-cua-arsenal-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-voi-roma-172-192633.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Roma</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-tuc-toi-coi-malcom-khong-ton-tai-tren-the-gioi-184-192490.html\">Roma t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1i coi Malcom kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/hlv-di-francesco-phat-bieu-ve-vu-roma-mua-hut-malcom-176-192485.html\">HLV Roma c\u1ea1n l\u1eddi khi nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi c\u00e1i t\u00ean Malcom</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-nhan-barca-muon-bo-qua-vu-malcom-vay-dua-messi-day-184-192094.html\">Roma nh\u1eafn Barca: \u201cMu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf qua v\u1ee5 Malcom, v\u1eady \u0111\u01b0a Messi \u0111\u00e2y\u201d</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5457","checkdouble":"194430"},{"date":"07:19 14/08","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p ch\u01b0a b\u1ecf \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a Giroud h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/doi-bong-phap-chua-bo-y-dinh-dua-giroud-hoi-huong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marseille mu\u1ed1n mua Olivier Giroud l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i t\u1eeb 3 tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Giroud t\u1ea1i Chelsea b\u1ea5p b\u00eanh</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olivier Giroud gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea t\u1eeb Arsenal \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018. N\u1eeda cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Antonio Conte, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Alvaro Morata.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng tr\u00f4i qua, Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111ang ch\u1edd Giroud. HLV Maurizio Sarri k\u1ebf nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd \u00f4ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cao 1m93.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marseille mu\u1ed1n mua Olivier Giroud h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marseille mu\u1ed1n mua Olivier Giroud h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/Marseille-muon-mua-Olivier-Giroud-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Giroud kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u1edbi Huddersfield Town, Sarri \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Giroud m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat n\u00e0o. Anh ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 nh\u00ecn Morata \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn vai tr\u00f2 trung phong.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMarseille mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Giroud</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u00f4ng tin Marseille mu\u1ed1n mua Olivier Giroud \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Giroud cua Phap\" title=\"Giroud cua Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Deschamps-len-tieng-bao-ve-Giroud-ve-kha-nang-ghi-ban-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Marseille mu\u1ed1n mua Olivier Giroud</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, trong c\u01a1n kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o gi\u1ecfi, Marseille ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1edf h\u1eefu Giroud. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u00ean t\u1eeb gi\u1edd cho t\u1edbi khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i. Ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Le10Sport c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Marseille s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Giroud c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri. N\u1ebfu tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb ng\u00f3 l\u01a1 t\u1ea1i Chelsea, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a anh h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng AC Milan v\u00e0 Atletico Madrid c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m cho Giroud.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-xit-chelsea-ky-hop-dong-voi-ac-milan-trong-vai-gio-toi-172-194417.html\">Bom x\u1ecbt Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi AC Milan trong v\u00e0i gi\u1edd t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-tiet-lo-ly-do-tu-choi-barca-va-mu-172-194408.html\">Willian ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barca v\u00e0 MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-xit-bakayoko-roi-chelsea-ngay-trong-tuan-nay-171-194367.html\">Bom x\u1ecbt r\u1eddi Chelsea ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tiet-lo-cuc-soc-vu-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-den-chelsea-172-194320.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-tiec-nuoi-khi-chelsea-khong-the-ky-hop-dong-voi-cai-ten-nay-172-194318.html\">HLV Sarri ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5456","checkdouble":"194425"}]}